inotify-tools
=============
Attention: Before you run 『configure』 in shell, you need to run 『autogen.sh』in shell firstly, that will generate the configure file. 
           Then you can refer to the file 'INSTALL' in the current folder to complete the installation. 

This is a package of some commandline utilities relating to inotify.

The general purpose of this package is to allow inotify's features to be used
from within shell scripts.  Read the man pages for further details.

